	(text_box "In Quartus \"Device and Pin Options,\" ensure that the configuration pins are set to \"As regular I/O\" after configuration, or the SPI logic won't be able to use DCLK and DATA0."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 46.99 346.71 0)
		(size 92.71 5.08)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
